{
  "stem": "20083.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "In fact, on September 1, we returned to Woking, Surrey, and read in the paper that Hitler had invaded Poland.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Then two days later, we listened at 10 o'clock in the morning or 11 o'clock in the morning Chamberlain declaring war on Hitler, on Nazi Germany because Hitler had not withdrawn his troops from Poland.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Absolutely, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not my father so much because he couldn't write anymore because of his stroke.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But my sister visited him and wrote to me about him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mother and I were constantly in touch by mail.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Unfortunately-- and I never forgive myself for it-- is every time I answered her letter I threw it away.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Of course today, it would be the most priceless things in my life.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I didn't realize, of course at the time, that war would break out, and that was that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we did correspond until, I think, the end of August.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then of course, everything was cut off because Germany-- or England declared war on Germany, and that was the end of that.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they gathered already that it looked very, very dangerous with Hitler invading all these different countries-- Austria and the Sudetenland and Danzig.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And after Danzig, I think, Chamberlain had already threatened Hitler with war if he invaded another country.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, of course, he did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in September when he moved into Poland-- and that was the end of it because Poland had never been German.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they declared war.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we didn't realize it-- it actually would occur.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We just knew there was a danger.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It might occur.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so did the English.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But they were totally unprepared as you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
